{"tid":553632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"31歲休班警搭地鐵圖偷16歲少女財物 潛逃一日落網","createTime":"2018-02-07T16:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-08T14:27:32.000Z","uid":5195,"like":64,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"78367aad52443ae3a26084c119b671f360ce5675","tid":553632,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T16:04:55.000Z","msg":"又有休班警員知法犯法！昨日傍晚6時許，警員在進行反罪惡巡邏期間，於一列由金鐘開往尖沙嘴的列車上發現一名男子形迹可疑，打開附近一名16歲非華裔少女的背包，其後於港鐵尖沙嘴站逃去。警方今晨於觀塘區拘捕一名31歲姓梁男子，經調查後得悉他為一名休班警員，以涉嫌「企圖盜竊」將他拘捕。被捕男子已獲准保釋候查，須於二月下旬向警方報到，案件交由油尖警區重案組第一隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。"},{"pid":"c2b87cdaf6a3938521af3e9e681aec68775e22b1","tid":553632,"uid":32473,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T16:06:09.000Z","msg":"屌樓豬個名"},{"pid":"8da49ebd122f1eab857a1dc9ea7215ec47afff9d","tid":553632,"uid":120070,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T16:07:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">休班狗</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc7c3743753cdf2a20779bbd483ac812a977c0c","tid":553632,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T16:15:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbca7cc38c37451b772aa271939ae96b508e5ca0","tid":553632,"uid":110964,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T16:17:20.000Z","msg":"警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇撚到識背啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63e1ce0ae73166b79264f318f60facbc052841ee","tid":553632,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T16:17:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"656f28041987ad4f16ee12560f545bf27588c896","tid":553632,"uid":88029,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"ci